OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain initially, turning heavy
OL,6,Fat times, combining with gales to
OL,7,Fbring decidedly un-Spring like
OL,8,Fweather. Clearing to blustery showers
OL,9,Faround mid-day, with outbreaks
OL,10,Foccasional in west, isolated with best
OL,11,Fof brightness in east. Showers turning
OL,12,Fwintry across higher ground.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers pushing across the
OL,15,Farea on strong west to southwest
OL,16,Fwinds. Outbreaks ranging from
OL,17,Foccasional in west and isolated around
OL,18,Fthe east coasts, also turning wintry
OL,19,Fto quite low levels.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,177,160,301,260,100,100
