OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers continuing, again
OL,6,Foccasional in west, isolated in east.
OL,7,FOutbreaks lighter than Thursday night
OL,8,Fwith sleet and snow increasingly
OL,9,Fconfined to higher areas. Best
OL,10,Fbrighter spells expected east of A9.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,13,Ffor Saturday again focused in west.
OL,14,FRain early Sunday, clearing to
OL,15,Fblustery showers by afternoon, wintry
OL,16,Facross hills. Scattered showers for
OL,17,FMonday, then periods of rain later in
OL,18,Fday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
